data.description: This charming 1950's shotgun style home offers a delightful blend of vintage appeal and modern comforts. Fully renovated over the years, it boasts updated electrical, plumbing, and a durable metal roof. Step into your home sweet home through the adorable front porch, radiating country charm. The kitchen is a standout feature, showcasing red cabinetry complemented by a tin feature wall and an inviting eat-in bar. Rustic charm permeates the space, accentuated by abundant natural light. The oversized primary suite provides a secluded retreat. Spacious enough for a seating area, the primary suite's bathroom combines old-world charm with rustic yet modern amenities, featuring a gorgeous double vanity, clawfoot tub, and a stand-alone shower. Situated on nearly an acre with a fenced space for your furry friends. The large covered back deck that overlooks the expansive backyard is perfect for relaxing or gatherings. This home is a unique blend of history and contemporary living, a must see!
